snippet.title: The Witcher 4 - Official Reveal Trailer | The Game Awards 2024
snippet.description:
The Witcher series returns with a new protagonist. CD Projekt Red's new RPG saga replaces Geralt with Ciri as the playable character to lead us into a new fantasy saga. From the developers of The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt and Cyberpunk 2077, CDPR give us our first glimpse into the world of The Witcher 4 as Ciri takes on a fearsome monster called the Bauk in this trailer pre-rendered in a custom build of Unreal Engine 5.

#IGN #Gaming #TheGameAwards

Harrdy Sandhu returns to Desi Melodies with "Tu Ru Ruu", following smash hits like "Bijlee Bijlee" and "Titliaan." Get ready to embrace the sizzle as Harrdy unveils his sexiest avatar yet, with his sheer appeal guaranteed to overwhelm your senses.

Penned and composed by the brilliant Sagar, and elevated by Bunny‚Äôs innovative production, "Tu Ru Ruu" is a groundbreaking sonic masterpiece. The visual experience is nothing short of spectacular, with Arvvindr S Khaira pushing boundaries once again to deliver a breathtaking short film that you‚Äôll find impossible to resist rewatching in a heartbeat.

Harrdy Sandhu continues to redefine Punjabi pop music‚Äîmixing sensuality with style‚Äîand crafting a song that's as bold, hot, and unforgettable as it gets.

[Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu]

Sohni ae than, Sohni jehi tu.

Mainu nasha chahdh ae.
[I‚Äôm feeling intoxicated.]

Ni taareya di loye, kariye romance,
[Under the starlight, let‚Äôs romance,]

Tu lagdi pari,
[You look like an angel,]

[Your fragrance is so beautiful.]

[I keep kissing your nose pin.]

Barf pai digdi, ni thand badi ae,
[The snow is falling, and it‚Äôs very cold,]

[I don‚Äôt want to catch a fever, darling.]

Ni weather ae minus 6 degree,
[The weather is minus 6 degrees,]

Ni aa ja aa ja, ik hoodie vich wadiye.
[Come on, let‚Äôs share one hoodie together.]

Tu uthi diggi jaye,
[You keep stumbling,]

Ni you so high.
[You‚Äôre so high.]

Je ho gaya kuch, baby don‚Äôt cry.
[If something happens, baby, don‚Äôt cry.]

What happens in Paris, stays in Paris‚Äîsun le tu.
[What happens in Paris, stays in Paris‚Äîlisten to me.]

Ni chal khadi o,
[Get up,]

Ni thand da hai time,
[It‚Äôs the time to chill,]

[Let‚Äôs go to Amsterdam.]

[My head spins,]

Ae tu chumeya, ya mainu hoya d√©j√† vu.

Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu
[Tuuuu Ruuu Ruuuuu]

snippet.title: Journey to the Center of the Earth (It Took 8 Days, I Lost 10kg)
snippet.description:
Join us on an extraordinary journey into the depths of Krubera Cave, the world‚Äôs deepest cave according to scientists. Over the course of 8 days, we venture into total darkness to determine its exact depth and uncover the secrets of this subterranean marvel.

Learn more about NVIDIA Studio ‚ñ∫ https://bit.ly/nvidiastudioruhi

Subscribe to Ruhi Cenet's YouTube Channel ‚ñ∫ https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Our expedition covers nearly 5 kilometers of rugged terrain, where we face extreme challenges, including losing an average of 10 kg per person. Along the way, we hope to discover new animal species that have been isolated for millions of years in this hidden world.

This is not just a journey; it‚Äôs a historic exploration into the unknown. Don‚Äôt miss the incredible story of survival, discovery, and human perseverance.

id.title: Perjalanan ke Pusat Bumi (Memakan Waktu 8 Hari, Saya Kehilangan 10 kg)
id.description:
Bergabunglah dengan kami dalam perjalanan luar biasa ke kedalaman Gua Krubera, gua terdalam di dunia menurut para ilmuwan. Selama 8 hari, kami menjelajah ke dalam kegelapan total untuk menentukan kedalamannya yang tepat dan mengungkap rahasia keajaiban bawah tanah ini.

Berlangganan Saluran YouTube Ruhi Cenet ‚ñ∫ https://goo.gl/MKi8tn

Ekspedisi kami mencakup hampir 5 kilometer medan terjal, tempat kami menghadapi tantangan ekstrem, termasuk kehilangan berat rata-rata 10 kg per orang. Sepanjang perjalanan, kami berharap dapat menemukan spesies hewan baru yang telah terisolasi selama jutaan tahun di dunia tersembunyi ini.

Ini bukan sekadar perjalanan; ini adalah eksplorasi bersejarah ke tempat yang tidak diketahui. Jangan lewatkan kisah luar biasa tentang bertahan hidup, penemuan, dan kegigihan manusia.

Terima kasih khusus kepada Universitas Federal Krimea, Masyarakat Geografis Rusia, ahli speleologi –ì–µ–Ω–Ω–∞–¥–∏–π –°–∞–º–æ—Ö–∏–Ω, –ü—ë—Ç—Ä –ö–æ–∑–∞—á—É–∫, –ê–ª—ë–Ω–∞ –¢–∏—â–µ–Ω–∫–æ, –ì—Ä–∏–≥–æ—Ä–∏–π –ì–∞–ø–µ–µ–Ω–∫–æ, –ï–≤–≥–µ–Ω–∏–π –ë–æ–≥–¥–∞–Ω–æ–≤, dan pelatih pribadi Ruhi Cenet, Ramazan Kaya.

snippet.title: Velaiyilla Pattathari Scene |‡Æ™‡Æø‡Æö‡Øç‡Æö‡Øà‡Æï‡Øç‡Æï‡Ææ‡Æ∞‡Æ©‡Ææ ‡Æá‡Æ∞‡ØÅ‡Æ®‡Øç‡Æ§‡Ææ‡Æ≤‡ØÅ‡ÆÆ‡Øç ‡Æé‡Æ©‡Æï‡Øç‡Æï‡ØÅ‡Æ©‡Øç‡Æ©‡ØÅ ‡Æí‡Æ∞‡ØÅ ‡ÆÖ‡Æü‡Øà‡ÆØ‡Ææ‡Æ≥‡ÆÆ‡Øç ‡Æá‡Æ∞‡ØÅ‡Æï‡Øç‡Æï‡ØÅ| Dhanush
snippet.description:
Velaiilla Pattadhari (transl.‚ÄâThe Unemployed Graduate), popularly referred to as VIP, is a 2014 Indian Tamil-language action drama film[3] written and directed by Velraj, in his directorial debut, and produced by Dhanush, who also enacts in the lead role alongside Amala Paul, Vivek, Saranya Ponvannan, Samuthirakani and Surbhi. It is the predecessor to Velaiilla Pattadhari 2 (2017), which was directed by Soundarya Rajinikanth; replacing Velraj. The film follows Raghuvaran "Raghu," an unemployed graduate, who tries to overcome various obstacles before and after finding employment.

Dhanush, besides acting, producing and distributing the venture in association with Escape Artists Motion Pictures, also worked as the lyricist and album producer on the film's original soundtrack. The film's album and score were composed by Anirudh Ravichander.The stunt department of this movie was handled by Hari Dinesh. Principal photography commenced in August 2013 and was completed by May 2014, with the film being shot primarily in Chennai. The film was released on 18 July 2014, and received a positive critical reception. It was remade in Kannada as Brihaspathi (2018).
